e medal\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the Romanian federation appealed against Jordan's, per theWashington Post.\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 500, \"end\": 508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"score\": 0.9985086968521484, \"rank\": 0.0008277920060903143, \"text\": \"Romanian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 537, \"end\": 543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9902630226171315, \"rank\": 0.005680197788554462, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theWashington Post\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The CAS then decided that Coach Landi's inquiry happened 1 minute and 4 seconds after the score was called (4 seconds after the 1-minute deadline).\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2654561267186714e-18, \"text\": \"CAS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Coach Landi's inquiry\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"the score\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1-minute deadline\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, Jordan's win was effectively reversed, with Ana being awarded bronze instead.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9902630226171315, \